  "abstract": "Because of a software problem at the Federal eRulemaking Portal (http://www.regulations.gov), the Board did not receive certain public comments submitted through that portal. This problem affected comments on four of the Board's proposed rules [Docket Nos. R-1286; R- 1314, R-1315; and R-1316] that were submitted only through the Federal eRulemaking Portal between March 22, 2008, and September 8, 2008. A total of 83 comments on the four proposals were not relayed to the Board. As set forth below,",
